Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:13.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\blur4}阴雨天的放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:19.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)\blur4}「这样如何」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:23.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,350)\blur4}你恶作剧般地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:24.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}飘飘然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:28.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}短发在风中摇曳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:33.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\blur4\an3}我们依然生活在孤独的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)\blur4\an3}小聪明与固执都会有个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:43.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\blur4}向着那颗星星前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:50.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即使再度迎来能够由衷地笑出来的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:54.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)\blur4}无光也无暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.88,0:22:58.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,350)\blur4}表里都是你
